quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  13,19,"E ko on annduЙ—o wonnde ko jippinaa kon e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maa ko goonga, wa'ata wa on Й“unЙ—o? Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraaЙ“e-haqqillaaji Й“en"
  13,20,"Й“en hunnooЙ“e ahadi Alla ndin, Й“e firtataa ahodal(hoolaare)"
  13,21,"e Й“en jokkooЙ“e kon ko Alla yamiri yo jokke, hiЙ“e hula Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e hula bonnde hasboore"
  13,22,"Й“en muГұГұoriiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yarluyee Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ГұiiЙ“ni julde, Й“e nafqii e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e, gunndoo e kene, hiЙ“e duГұira moЖҙЖҙere nden bone on. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e battane galle"
  13,23,"Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, hiЙ“e naata Й—i, e Й“en moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e geyngolji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Hara Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en hino naatirana Й“e kala damal"
  13,24,"Kisal wonii e mo'on, sabu muГұal mon ngal. Battane galle Й—en moЖҙЖҙii"
  13,25,"ЖҒen (non) firtooЙ“e ahadi Alla ndin Й“aawo fiЙ“ugol ndi, hiЙ“e taЖҙoo e ko Alla yamiri kon yo jokke, hiЙ“e bonna ka leydi, Й“e Й—on, hino woodani Й“e kuЙ—di, hino woodani Й“e kadi bonЙ—um galle"
  13,26,"Alla no yaГұГұana arsike on Mo O muuyi, Himo Й“ittina. HiЙ“e weltora nguurndam aduna, nguurndam aduna non wonaali ka laakara, si wanaa dakamme-hoy"
  13,27,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e no wi'a: \"Ko haЙ—no Aaya jippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Maaku: \"Alla majjinay tun mo O muuyi, O fewna e Makko on tuubuЙ—o-ruttii"
  13,28,"Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e Й“erЙ—e mun deeЖҙirta jantagol Alla. Anndee ko jantagol Alla ngol Й“erЙ—e Й—en deeЖҙirta"
